id: pmc-ew5n
title: Add --item-url-base to release.yml changelog generation steps
description: The release workflow ran node dist/cli.js directly with hardcoded flags that did not include --item-url-base. Updated all three changelog generation calls in release.yml to include --item-url-base so CI produces the same linked format as the local npm run changelog script.
type: Chore
status: closed
priority: 0
tags[3]: changelog,ci,links
created_at: "2026-05-24T12:36:17.959Z"
updated_at: "2026-05-24T12:36:33.322Z"
deadline: "2026-05-24T00:00:00.000Z"
author: codex
estimated_minutes: 10
acceptance_criteria: release.yml includes --item-url-base in all three changelog generation calls; CI-generated CHANGELOG.md has clickable links for all pm item IDs.
reviewer: steve
risk: low
confidence: high
sprint: 2026-05-production
release: v2026.05.24-8
resolution: Added --item-url-base to all three node dist/cli.js calls in .github/workflows/release.yml.
expected_result: CI-generated CHANGELOG.md has clickable item ID links; release.yml check step passes.
actual_result: "release.yml updated; npm run changelog:check passes locally confirming format is consistent."
