notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-24T12:36:17.959Z",codex,"Discovered after v2026.05.24-7 CI release: CHANGELOG showed plain IDs not links because workflow did not have --item-url-base."
learnings[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-24T12:36:17.959Z",codex,"When adding new CLI flags to npm scripts, always audit CI workflow files for hardcoded node dist/cli.js calls that bypass npm scripts and need manual update."
